{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-42","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 42","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete postaviti ponašanje pregledača dodavanjem komponenti za <code>meta</code> unutar <code>head</code>. Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;meta attribute=\"value\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar elementa <code>head</code>, postavite unutar element <code>meta</code> sa atributom element <code>charset</code> koji je postavljen na vrednost <code>utf-8</code>. Ovo govori pretraživaču kako da dekodira znakove za stranicu.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da je element <code>meta</code> tipa void.</p>\n<p>Sa tim poslednjim promenama, završili ste radionicu Cat Photo App. Čestitam!</p>\n</section>","id":"62bb4009e3458a128ff57d5d","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-42"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    \n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[3,5],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da kreirate element <code>meta</code> unutar elementa <code>head</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('head > meta'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi mu dodeliti atribut elementu <code>charset</code> sa vrednošću <code>UTF-8</code> na element <code>meta</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelector('head > meta')?.getAttribute('charset')?.toLowerCase(), 'utf-8');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj element <code>meta</code> treba da bude prazan (void) element; nije ti potrebno dodavati <code>&#x3C;/meta></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /<\\/meta\\s*>?/i);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-42","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopPr